While working on this topic, I was surprised to see how common online scams have become, especially in India. Many people lose money not because of complex hacking, but due to small mistakes like trusting unknown links or sharing OTPs. I didn’t realize earlier how risky it can be to accept random UPI requests or click on messages that look genuine.

This made me more aware of my own online habits. One thing I will definitely change is being more careful before clicking on any link or making online payments. I will always check the details properly and avoid trusting unknown sources. This topic helped me understand that staying safe online is mostly about being alert and thinking before acting.
